README 
======

1. This test artifact is a real use case use with salesforce connector in esb.
2. This api query salesforce user information and transform a json object using payload factory mediator.
3. This can be used to test   <payloadFactory media-type="json">

Steps :

1. Salesforce connector should be installed and enabled
2. MySFConfig local entry should have been created with salesforce credentials
E.g.,

<salesforce.init>
    <username>xxxx@abc.com</username>
    <password>xxxxx</password>
    <loginUrl>https://login.salesforce.com/services/Soap/u/34.0</loginUrl>
</salesforce.init>

3. Users should have been created in the salesforce account and profile id should be set in the below property

<property name="ProfileId" value="00e90000001aVwiAAE" scope="default" type="STRING"/>
